 17 Juli 1916 Monday Rain all night , slept in hut on bumpi ground . Feel good , pack not so heavi . discard more of my belong at last place . Stay in our billet all day . Hut unhealthi , damp mould on ground . Pay in afternoon . 40 franc . Short ration for tea , go down to villag supplement same with egg and cafe . Mud slush on road veri slipperi . Talk with some French soldier . Mutual effort to speak each other lingo . not too success . Impromptu concert in hut on return
